---
title: Summer Pesto Risoni Salad with Charred Corn & Goat Cheese
description: Risoni – the clever pasta that looks like rice – is the ideal ingredient in this dinnertime salad. With baby spinach and snow peas, this fresh bowl of goodness gets the welcome addition of goat cheese and pesto to really raise the flavour stakes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c074850e3f3393dcc1767a2-142b4b4b.jpg
